T1  - Inside-Out, Outside-In, or All-in-One? The Role of Network Sequencing in the Elaboration of Ideas
AU  - Ter Wal, Anne L. J.
AU  - Criscuolo, Paola
AU  - Salter, Ammon
Y1  - 2022/01/13
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2023/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2020.1231
DO  - 10.5465/amj.2020.1231
T2  - Academy of Management Journal
JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 432
